%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22YouTuber%20helps%20researchers%20solve%20the%20mystery%20of%20a%202%2C000-year-old%20'computer'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222194%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22antikythera%20mechanism%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5760c14952bcd022008c9403%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222211%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20fragment%20of%20the%202%2C200-year-old%20Antikythera%20Mechanism%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20earliest%20surviving%20mechanical%20computing%20device%2C%20is%20seen%20at%20the%20National%20Archaeological%20Museum%20in%20Athens.%3Cp%3EAssociated%20Press%2FThanassis%20Stavrakis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EResearchers%20think%20they've%20solved%20the%202%2C200-year-old%20mystery%20of%20the%20Antikythera%20mechanism.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20ancient%20device%2C%20found%20in%20a%20shipwreck%2C%20likely%20followed%20a%20Greek%20lunar%20calendar.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20used%20statistical%20modeling%20techniques%20typically%20used%20to%20study%20ripples%20in%20space-time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Graham%20Woan%20knew%20just%20how%20he%20wanted%20to%20spend%20his%20Christmas%20break%3A%20trying%20to%20solve%20the%202%2C200-year-old%20mystery%20of%20the%20oldest%20known%20%26quot%3Bcomputer%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnown%20as%20the%20Antikythera%20mechanism%2C%20the%20bronze%20device%20is%20a%20mechanical%20computer%20with%20interlocking%20gears.%20In%20the%20second%20century%20BCE%2C%20a%20user%20would%20have%20used%20its%20rings%20and%20evenly%20spaced%20holes%20to%20chart%20future%20celestial%20events%2C%20such%20as%20eclipses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20many%20of%20those%20evenly%20spaced%20holes%20existed%20has%20been%20a%20mystery%20and%20holds%20the%20key%20to%20determining%20exactly%20how%20the%20computer%20functioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTuber%20Chris%20Budiselic%20has%20long%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbhi.co.uk%2Fby-the-light-of-the-moon-a-lunar-calendar-on-the-antikythera-mechanism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efascinated%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20mechanism%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DML4tw_UzqZE%26list%3DPLZioPDnFPNsHnyxfygxA0to4RXv4_jDU2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%3C%2Fa%3E%20creating%20his%20own%20version%20seven%20years%20ago%20but%20wasn't%20sure%20how%20many%20holes%20to%20include.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20some%20of%20Budisic's%20published%20research%2C%20University%20of%20Glasgow%20astronomers%2C%20including%20Woan%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eturned%20to%20statistical%20modeling%20techniques%20to%20find%20the%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20struck%20me%20as%20an%20interesting%20problem%2C%20and%20one%20that%20I%20thought%20I%20might%20be%20able%20to%20solve%20in%20a%20different%20way%20during%20the%20Christmas%20holidays%2C%20so%20I%20set%20about%20using%20some%20statistical%20techniques%20to%20answer%20the%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20Woan%20said%20in%20a%20university%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gla.ac.uk%2Fnews%2Fheadline_1086643_en.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20number%20of%20holes%2C%20the%20researchers%20found%2C%20the%20device%20follows%20a%20lunar%20calendar%20instead%20of%20an%20Egyptian%20one%2C%20as%20some%20previous%20research%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288229c20-3e52-49a3-ac2a-ac07f07cf6a4%5C%22%3EA%20shipwreck%20full%20of%20ancient%20treasures%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225354%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22antikythera%20mechanism%20analog%20ancient%20greece%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5760c507dd0895ac7a8b4972%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223569%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Antikythera%20mechanism%20is%20broken%20and%20eroded%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20know%20exactly%20how%20it%20worked.%3Cp%3EAssociated%20Press%2FPetros%20Giannakouris%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Antikythera%20mechanism%20is%20just%20one%20intriguing%20finding%20from%20a%202%2C000-year-old%20shipwreck%20that%20divers%20first%20discovered%20in%201900.%20Divers%20waiting%20out%20a%20storm%20found%20the%20remains%20near%20the%20Greek%20island%20of%20Antikythera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExcavations%20have%20uncovered%20three%20life-size%20marble%20horse%20statues%2C%20coins%2C%20jewelry%2C%20and%20other%20treasures%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whoi.edu%2Fknow-your-ocean%2Focean-topics%2Focean-human-lives%2Funderwater-archaeology%2Fantikythera-shipwreck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWoods%20Hole%20Oceanographic%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20the%20Antikythera%20mechanism%20is%20perhaps%20the%20most%20unique%20discovery%20of%20them%20all.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt's%20about%20the%20size%20of%20a%20shoebox%2C%20is%20broken%20into%20six%20pieces%2C%20and%20has%20eroded%20from%20its%20time%20underwater.%20The%20mechanism%20is%20so%20sophisticated%20that%20some%20thought%20it%20had%20to%20be%20a%20modern%20device%20that%20got%20mixed%20in%20with%20the%20ancient%20artifacts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F1006146%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20Derek%20John%20de%20Solla%20Price.%20He%20helped%20discover%20the%20device's%20function%20in%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EX-ray%20images%20from%202005%20gave%20researchers%20new%20details%20about%20the%20device.%20And%20in%202020%2C%20Budiselic%20and%20his%20colleagues%20used%20the%20images%20to%20measure%20the%20positions%20of%20the%20holes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbhi.co.uk%2Fantikytheramechanism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20mechanism%20had%20between%20347%20and%20367%20holes.%20If%20it%20had%20closer%20to%20350%20holes%2C%20it%20would%20have%20followed%20the%20lunar%20calendar.%20If%20it%20had%20365%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20modeled%20on%20the%20Egyptian%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20nail%20down%20an%20exact%20number%20because%20of%20the%20device's%20diminished%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20learning%20about%20Budiselic's%20research%2C%20Woan%20first%20used%20Bayesian%20analysis%2C%20calculating%20different%20probabilities%20of%20the%20total%20number%20of%20holes%20based%20on%20the%20position%20and%20number%20of%20holes%20in%20the%20remaining%20pieces%20of%20bronze.%20He%20learned%20that%20it%20was%20hundreds%20of%20times%20more%20likely%20that%20the%20device%20had%20354%20holes%20than%20360%20holes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWoan's%20colleague%20Joseph%20Bayley%20followed%20up%20the%20research%20by%20modifying%20techniques%20used%20to%20study%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fligo-gravitational-wave-detector-more-powerful-squeezing-light-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egravitational%20waves%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20ripples%20in%20space-time.%20His%20results%20agreed%20with%20Woan's%3B%20there%20were%20likely%20either%20354%20or%20355%20holes%20in%20the%20ring.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20there's%20a%20much%20higher%20probability%20that%20the%20mechanism%20tracked%20the%20Greek%20lunar%20year%20instead%20of%20the%20Egyptian%20one.%20It%20was%20capable%20of%20calculating%20planets'%20positions%20incredibly%20accurately%20for%20its%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20finding%20reinforces%20the%20impressive%20craftsmanship%20and%20knowledge%20it%20took%20to%20create%20the%20device.%20%26quot%3BThe%20precision%20of%20the%20holes'%20positioning%20would%20have%20required%20highly%20accurate%20measurement%20techniques%20and%20an%20incredibly%20steady%20hand%20to%20punch%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Bayley%20said%20in%20the%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20have%20published%20their%20research%20in%20the%20peer-reviewed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbhi.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F07-HJJuly24-AOTM-2.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHorological%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fantikythera-mechanism-mystery-gravitational-waves-calendar-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720138180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66870c1f1f0c1cd6d731a9a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fantikythera-mechanism-mystery-gravitational-waves-calendar-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Antikythera%20mechanism%20was%20discovered%20over%20100%20years%20ago.%20Researchers%20think%20they%20solved%20the%20ancient%20computer's%20mystery%20with%20statistical%20techniques.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jmcgrath%40insider.com%20(Jenny%20McGrath)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fantikythera-mechanism-mystery-gravitational-waves-calendar-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tiago%20PZK%20Drops%20%E2%80%98Gotti%20A%E2%80%99%20With%20Features%20From%20Nicki%20Nicole%2C%20Manuel%20Turizo%2C%20Trueno%20and%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720137600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F520d504e-ea30-869f-efe2-e85b708dee7b-2.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236060341%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Argentine%20rapper%20and%20singer%20Tiago%20PZK%20has%20dropped%20his%20star-studded%20sophomore%20album%2C%20%E2%80%9CGotti%20A.%E2%80%9D%20The%2014-song%20collection%20boasts%20features%20from%20fellow%20Argentine%20music%20stars%20like%20Nicki%20Nicole%2C%20Duki%20and%20Trueno%2C%20along%20with%20Manuel%20Turizo%20and%20Justin%20Quiles.%20Executively%20produ