0the%20major%20international%20issues%20it%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20China%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELabour%20would%20undertake%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull%20audit%26quot%3B%20across%20all%20government%20departments%20of%20the%20UK's%20relationship%20with%20China%20to%20%26quot%3Bset%20the%20direction%20and%20course%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20China%20policy%2C%20Lammy%20told%20reporters%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarmer%20last%20year%20said%20the%20UK%20needed%20to%20%26quot%3Bwean%20itself%20off%26quot%3B%20China%20on%20issues%20like%20trade%2C%20commerce%20and%20technology%20while%20acknowledging%20the%20importance%20of%20being%20able%20to%20cooperate%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20tackling%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20will%20be%20to%20balance%20the%20UK's%20trade%20and%20economic%20interests%20with%20security%20imperatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20be%20complicated%20by%20a%20possible%20return%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20Washington%20after%20the%20US%20presidential%20election%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20would%20be%20expected%20to%20ramp%20up%20pressure%20on%20allies%20to%20be%20tougher%20with%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Israel-Palestinian%20conflict%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELabour%20says%20it%20is%20committed%20to%20recognising%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20contribution%20to%20a%20renewed%20peace%20process%20which%20results%20in%20a%20two-state%20solution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20has%20not%20set%20out%20any%20timescale%20for%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20commitments%20include%20pushing%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%2C%20the%20release%20of%20all%20hostages%20and%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20amount%20of%20aid%20getting%20into%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Europe%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarmer%20has%20pledged%20to%20work%20with%20France's%20far-right%20National%20Rally%20(RN)%20party%20if%20it%20wi