C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111495459.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENag%20Ashwin's%20'Kalki%202898%20AD%2C'%20starring%20Prabhas%2C%20Deepika%20Padukone%2C%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20and%20Kamal%20Haasan%2C%20saw%20a%202%25%20dip%20in%20collections%2C%20grossing%20Rs%20414.25%20crore%20in%20India%20and%20surpassing%20Rs%20700%20crore%20globally.%20Ashwin%20mentioned%20shooting%20for%2025-30%20days%20with%20pending%20action%20scenes%20for%20the%20sequel%2C%20emphasizing%20a%20showdown%20involving%20Yaskin%2C%20Karna%2C%20and%20Ashwatthama.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fkalki-2898-ad-box-office-collection-day-8-the-prabhas-and-deepika-padukone-starrer-collects-rs-414-25-crore-in-its-first-week%2Farticleshow%2F111495459.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDon't%20Know%20Where%20He%20Is%2C%20Don't%20Need%20To%26quot%3B%3A%20Bhole%20Baba's%20Lawyer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaking%20a%20late-night%20appearance%20outside%20the%20ashram%20in%20Mainpuri%20where%20Bhole%20Baba%20aka%20Narayan%20Saakar%20Hari%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20staying%2C%20the%20self-styled%20godman's%20lawyer%20said%20he%20does%20not%20know%20where%20he%20is%20and%20does%20not%20need%20to%20know%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepeating%20the%20claim%20that%20anti-social%20elements%20caused%20the%20stampede%20at%20the%20religious%20event%20organised%20in%20the%20godman's%20honour%20in%20Hathras%2C%20in%20which%20121%20people%20were%20killed%2C%20the%20lawyer%20also%20said%20the%20baba%20is%20a%20follower%20of%20the%20law%20and%20will%20not%20go%20on%20the%20run.%20The%20original%20name%20of%20the%20'godman'%20is%20Suraj%20Pal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20hired%20by%20Pal%20is%20AP%20Singh%2C%20who%20has%20defended%20Nirbhaya%20gangrape%20convicts%2C%20represented%20Seema%20Haider%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20woman%20who%20crossed%20over%20into%20India%20illegally%2C%20and%20appeared%20on%20behalf%20of%20farm%20unions%20during%20the%20farmers'%20protests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20reporters%20outside%20the%20ashram%20on%20Thursday%20night%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20where%20he%20(Pal)%20is%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20know.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20do%20my%20work...%20As%20soon%20as%20I%20find%20out%2C%20I%20will%20tell%20you...%20How%20can%20I%20or%20you%20say%20he%20is%20responsible...%20From%20what%20I%20have%20found%20out%20about%20Narayan%20Saakar%20Hari%2C%20he%20is%20not%20going%20to%20go%20on%20the%20run.%20He%20is%20a%20follower%20of%20the%20law%2C%20he%20believes%20in%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20constitution.%20He%20will%20be%20in%20an%20ashram%2C%20not%20a%20hotel.%20He%20doesn't%20stay%20at%20a%20hotel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20events%20of%20Tuesday%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20the%20%3Cem%3E'satsang'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(religious%20event)%20was%20organised%20in%20an%20open%20area%20with%20fields%20everywhere%20and%20reports%20of%20a%20closed%20space%20were%20untrue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spoke%20to%20people%20who%20attended%20the%20%3Cem%3E'satsang'%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Elderly%20women%20who%20were%20injured%20told%20me%20something%20like%20this%20has%20never%20happened%20before.%20They%20said%20they%20had%20been%20attending%20the%20%3Cem%3E'satsangs'%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%2015-18%20years%20and%20they%20were%20held%20every%20Tuesday%2C%20barring%20a%20few%20weeks%20in%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20The%20women%20told%20me%20the%20men%20who%20crushed%20people%20were%20well-built%2C%20seemed%20drunk%20and%20started%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20saw%20an%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20them%20how%20long%20it%20had%20been%20since%20Narayan%20Saakar%20Hari%20left%20and%20they%20said%2030-35%20minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20many%20of%20the%20organisers%20and%20volunteers%20also%20left%20their%20loved%20ones%2C%20including%20their%20children%2C%20mothers%20and%20wives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20administration%20was%20at%20fault%20because%20permission%20was%20given%20to%20hold%20an%20event%20near%20a%20highway%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20question%20does%20not%20arise%20because%20no%20traffic%20accidents%20took%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20also%20brushed%20away%20a%20reporter's%20query%20on%20Pal's%20followers%20calling%20the%20'godman'%20a%20%3Cem%3E'parmatma'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(immortal%20soul)%20and%20said%20he%20was%20one%20too%2C%20because%20he%20had%20a%20soul%20which%20was%20also%20immortal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPal's%20Arrest%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIssuing%20a%20brief%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20maintaining%20silence%20since%20the%20stampede%2C%20Pal%20expressed%20his%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims%20and%20said%20he%20will%20take%20legal%20action%20against%20%26quot%3Banti-social%20elements%26quot%3B%20that%20were%20allegedly%20behind%20the%20tragedy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20Pal%20would%20be%20arrested%2C%20Inspector%20General%20(Aligarh%20Range)%20Shalabh%20Mathur%20had%20said%20earlier%20on%20Thursday%20that%20he%20was%20not%20named%20in%20the%20first%20information%20report%20and%20the%20police%20would%20take%20further%20action%20based%20on%20the%20facts%20that%20emerge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20make%20arrests%20based%20on%20what%20the%20investigation%20reveals...%20We%20will%20question%20the%20baba%20if%20necessary%2C%20it%20is%20too%20early%20to%20say%20or%20comment%20whether%20he%20has%20a%20role.%20He%20has%20not%20been%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20which%20has%20held%20the%20organisers%20responsibl