ews%2Ftata-hitachi-s-success-harvest-from-field-to-factory-in-west-bengal-124070401103_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Ftata-hitachi-s-success-harvest-from-field-to-factory-in-west-bengal-124070401103_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLoopholes%20And%20Lapses%26quot%3B%3A%20Court%20Raps%20Gujarat%20Over%20Rajkot%20Gaming%20Zone%20Fire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20again%20rapped%20the%20state%20government%20over%20the%20Rajkot%20game%20zone%20fire%20that%20killed%2027%20persons%20in%20May%2C%20wondering%20why%20a%20demolition%20order%20against%20the%20illegal%20structure%20was%20not%20executed%20for%20nearly%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20censure%20came%20in%20response%20to%20an%20affidavit%20submitted%20to%20the%20division%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20Sunita%20Agarwal%20and%20Justice%20Pranav%20Trivedi%20that%20has%20been%20hearing%20a%20suo%20motu%20PIL%20(public%20interest%20litigation)%20it%20had%20taken%20up%20on%20May%2026%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20government%20on%20Thursday%20also%20submitted%20its%20%26quot%3Bfact-finding%20inquiry%26quot%3B%20report%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20to%20the%20HC%20on%20the%20TRP%20game%20zone%20blaze%20in%20Rajkot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20last%20month%20had%20expressed%20displeasure%20over%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20fire%20and%20ordered%20a%20%26quot%3Bfact-finding%20inquiry%26quot%3B%20to%20uncover%20how%20the%20illegal%20game%20zone%20had%20come%20up%20and%20what%20roles%20officials%20played%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20had%20prompted%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20to%20appoint%20a%20%26quot%3Bfact-finding%20committee%26quot%3B%20comprising%20IAS%20officers%20Manisha%20Chandra%20(Commissioner%20of%20Rural%20Development)%2C%20P%20Swaroop%20(Commissioner%20of%20Land%20Reforms)%20and%20Rajkumar%20Beniwal%20(Vice%20Chairman%20%26amp%3B%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%2C%20Gujarat%20Maritime%20Board).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20going%20through%20the%20state's%20affidavit%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20chief%20justice%20said%20though%20the%20officials%20of%20the%20Rajkot%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(RMC)%20were%20aware%20that%20the%20TRP%20game%20zone%20was%20illegal%2C%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20against%20it%20despite%20a%20demolition%20order%20being%20served%20to%20the%20management%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20demolition%20order%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20RMC.%20One%20year%20has%20passed%20since%20then%20(till%20the%20fire%20incident).%20Why%20was%20it%20not%20executed%3F%20Where%20is%20the%20answer%3F%20That%20demolition%20order%20proves%20that%20officials%20knew%20that%20the%20structure%20was%20illegal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CJ%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Advocate%20General%20Kamal%20Trivedi%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20present%20Municipal%20Commissioner%20has%20already%20suspended%20RMC's%20Town%20Planning%20Officer%20(TPO)%20and%20an%20Assistant%20TPO%20for%20negligence%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Agarwal%20said%20it%20was%20not%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20action%20against%20a%20few%20people%20will%20not%20help%20you.%20The%20working%20(style)%20has%20to%20be%20revisited.%20There%20are%20loopholes%20and%20lapses%20which%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20care%20of.%20You%20cannot%20put%20this%20state%20in%20this%20situation.%20It%20is%20very%20serious%20that%20such%20incidents%20are%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20noted%20the%20chief%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20expressed%20displeasure%20over%20the%20state%20government's%20submission%20that%20the%20then%20Rajkot%20municipal%20commissioner%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20illegal%20structure%20because%20TPO%20and%20his%20office%20were%20dealing%20with%20the%20matter%20and%20the%20demolition%20notice%20was%20sent%20by%20TPO%2C%20not%20the%20civic%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20say%20that%20this%20was%20not%20brought%20to%20my%20notice.%20It's%20not%20an%20excuse.%20Even%20I%20can't%20say%20that.%20I%20have%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20everything%2C%20good%20or%20bad.%20This%20should%20be%20the%20approach%20of%20the%20head%20of%20an%20institution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CJ%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20a%20report%20from%20the%20state%20government-appointed%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20is%20still%20pending%2C%20the%20court%20has%20asked%20Mr%20Trivedi%20to%20submit%20it%20as%20well%20as%20an%20Action%20Taken%20Report%20on%20July%2025%2C%20when%20the%20matter%20will%20be%20heard%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-seven%20persons%2C%20including%20four%20children%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20massive%20fire%20that%20swept%20through%20the%20game%20zone%20in%20the%20Nana-Mava%20locality%20of%20Rajkot%20city%20on%20May%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20probe%20revealed%20that%20the%20game%20zone%20was%20running%20without%20any%20no%20objection%20certificate%20(NOC)%20from%20the%20fire%20department%20of%20the%20RMC.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720114800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fepqnmvio_rajkot-fire-_625x300_27_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Floopholes-and-lapses-high-court-raps-gujarat-over-rajkot-gaming-zone-fire-6035627%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20again%20rebuked%20the%20state%20government%20over%20the%20Rajkot%20game%20zone%20fire%20that%20killed%2027%20persons%20in%20May%2C%20wondering%20why%20a%20demolition%20order%20against%20the%20illegal%20structure%20was%20not%20executed%20for%20nearly%20a%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Floopholes-and-lapses-high-court-raps-gujarat-over-rajkot-gaming-zone-fire-6035627%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc