ars%20that%20I%20have%20seen%20Rohit%20show%20so%20much%20emotion.%20When%20we%20were%20climbing%20those%20steps%20(at%20Kensington%20Oval)%20he%20was%20crying%20and%20I%20was%20crying%2C%26quot%3B%20Kohli%20said%20during%20the%20ceremony%20after%20a%20memorable%20open%20bus%20victory%20parade.%20On%20this%20very%20ground%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20Kohli%20had%20said%20that%20it%20was%20only%20fair%20to%20carry%20the%20maestro%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20on%20their%20shoulders%20after%20he%20carried%20the%20burden%20of%20Indian%20cricket%20for%2021%20years.%20Now%20at%2035%2C%20standing%20on%20the%20same%20hallowed%20turf%2C%20Kohli%2C%20who%20announced%20his%20retirement%20from%20the%20shortest%20format%20after%20the%20trophy%20was%20sealed%20last%20week%2C%20%26quot%3Bhoped%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20and%20his%20skipper%20had%20done%20well%20enough%20to%20carry%20the%20burden%20for%2015%20years%20and%20bring%20the%20'Cup'%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20we%20(Rohit%20and%20I)%20have%20carried%20the%20burden%20and%20no%20better%20to%20bring%20it%20(trophy)%20back%20here%20(Wankhede)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kohli%2C%20who%20knew%20during%20the%20innings%20break%20of%20the%20final%20that%20this%20was%20his%20last%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHalfway%20through%20the%20game%20I%20knew%20it%20it%20was%20time%20and%20let%20the%20next%20generation%20take%20over%2C%20%26quot%3Badded%20Kohli%2C%20sharing%20a%20sentiment%20that%20he%20had%20voiced%20after%20the%20final%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20youngest%20member%20of%20the%20class%20of%202011%2C%20he%20had%20seen%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20Harbhajan%20Singh%20and%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20teary-eyed%2C%20soaked%20in%20emotion%20and%20perhaps%2C%20he%20never%20understood%20where%20was%20it%20all%20pent%20up.%20But%20now%20he%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20connect%20with%20the%20emotions%20of%20the%20senior%20players%20who%20cried%20that%20night%20but%20now%20I%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Indian%20cricket%20team's%20current%20elder%20statesman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20lighter%20note%2C%20when%20the%20programme%20emcee%20Gaurav%20Kapoor%20asked%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20thinking%20of%20signing%20a%20petition%20to%20declare%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20as%20a%20national%20treasure.%20Will%20you%20sign%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20sign%20it%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20pat%20came%20the%20reply%20from%20the%20legend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBumrah%20is%20a%20once%20in%20a%20generation%20player%20and%20so%20glad%20he%20plays%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Kohli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20to%20witness%20such%20frenzy%20was%20once%20in%20a%20lifetime%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20ground%20is%20really%20special.%20Came%20here%20as%20a%20kid%20and%20what%20I%20saw%20today%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20something%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeeing%20my%20son%2C%20I%20was%20emotional%20and%20I%20didn't%20have%20words.%20Told%20my%20wife%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20my%20son%20(see%20me%20playing).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sentiment%20was%20echoed%20by%20outgoing%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20going%20to%20miss%20this%20love.%20What%20I%20saw%20on%20streets%20tonight%2C%20I%20won't%20forget%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20hoarse%20voice%2C%20having%20lost%20it%20while%20screaming%20in%20excitement%20through%20the%20parade.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720113300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fjlqmmcko_cs_625x300_04_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Ffirst-time-in-15-years-virat-kohlis-heartwarming-revelation-about-rohit-sharma-6035339%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20had%20never%20seen%20%26quot%3Ban%20emotional%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20Sharma%20in%20their%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20old%20association%20till%20the%20Indian%20captain%20hugged%20him%20wi