dor%20police%20free%2049%20people%20held%20by%20gang%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720111683000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F162e%2Flive%2Fb718e470-3a19-11ef-944b-53ebccb147ed.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcy9487g0y8yo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Police%20seize%20dynamite%2C%20weapons%20and%20ammunitions%20during%20a%20raid%20of%20tunnels%20in%20a%20mining%20area.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcy9487g0y8yo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcy9487g0y8yo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcy9487g0y8yo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Senior%20Lawyer%20Points%20To%20'China%20Link'%20In%20Hindenburg's%20Attack%20On%20Adani%20Group%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20stunning%20claim%20that%20he%20has%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmoking%20gun%26quot%3B%2C%20senior%20lawyer%20Mahesh%20Jethmalani%20has%20alleged%20that%20a%20businessman%20with%20Chinese%20links%20had%20commissioned%20the%20report%20by%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20which%20led%20to%20shares%20of%20Adani%20Group%20companies%20taking%20a%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20had%20said%20that%20foreign%20portfolio%20investor%20Kingdon%20Capital%20Management%20LLC%20and%20its%20entities%20aided%20Hindenburg%20in%20indirectly%20participating%20in%20Adani%20Enterprises%20Ltd.%20An%20investigation%20by%20the%20markets%20regulator%20also%20exposed%20that%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20and%20Hindenburg%20conspired%20together%20to%20take%20short%20positions%20in%20Adani%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20lengthy%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Jethmalani%20said%20Mark%20Kingdon%2C%20the%20American%20businessman%20behind%20Kingdon%20Capital%20Management%20LLC%2C%20had%20hired%20Hindenburg%20to%20prepare%20a%20report%20on%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20Mr%20Kingdon%20also%20approached%20Kotak's%20international%20investment%20arm%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Investments%20Limited%20(KMIL)%20to%20set%20up%20an%20offshore%20fund%20as%20well%20as%20offshore%20accounts%20to%20trade%20in%20Adani%20shares.%20This%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20Kotak%20India%20Opportunity%20Fund%20(KIOF).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20fund%20allegedly%20took%20short%20positions%20in%20shares%20of%20Adani%20Group%20Companies%20through%20the%20Mauritius%20route%20before%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20was%20made%20public%20and%20nearly%20%24%2040%20million%20for%20this%20was%20given%20by%20the%20Kingdon%20Master%20Fund.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20smoking%20gun%20referred%20to%20by%20the%20senior%20lawyer%20was%20his%20revelation%20that%20Mr%20Kingdon's%20wife%20Anla%20Cheng%2C%20a%20Chinese-American%20who%20has%20a%20large%20shareholding%20in%20the%20Kingdon%20Master%20Fund%2C%20is%20a%20lobbyist%20for%20Chinese%20interests%20in%20the%20United%20States.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20the%20CEO%20of%20%23SupChina%20a%20pro-China%20media%20corporate%20initiative%20which%20morphed%20into%20an%20entity%20called%20The%20China%20Project%20after%20a%20whistleblower%20accused%20SupChina%20of%20news%20subversion%20in%20China's%20interest%20in%20a%20sworn%20statement%20before%20the%20US%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%23TheChinaProject%20shut%20down%20after%20calls%20for%20an%20investigation%20into%20its%20subversive%20activities%20by%20some%20US%20senators%20including%20having%20links%20with%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party.%20The%20latter%20clearly%20has%20a%20bone%20to%20pick%20with%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jethmalani%20suggested%20that%20the%20actions%20of%20Ms%20Cheng%20and%20Mr%20Kingdon%20were%20prompted%20by%20the%20Adani%20Group%20thwarting%20Chinese%20interests%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20globe%2C%20including%20outbidding%20Chinese%20players%20for%20the%20Haifa%20Port%20in%20Israel%20and%20for%20coal%20projects%20near%20Sri%20Lanka's%20Jaffna.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Questions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20laid%20out%20his%20points%2C%20Mr%20Jethmalani%20posed%20three%20major%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20introduced%20the%20Kingdons%20to%20KMIL%2C%20what%20due%20diligence%20was%20conducted%20by%20KMIL%20regarding%20the%20Kingdons%20and%20did%20it%20participate%20in%20the%20short%20sell%20as%20a%20principal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20question%20was%20whether%20all%20the%20Indian%20people%2C%20organisations%20and%20entities%20who%20helped%20Hindenburg%20knew%20about%20the%20short-selling%20plan%20and%20whether%20they%20benefited%20from%20it.%20Mr%20Jethmalani%20specifically%20mentioned%20politicians%2C%20in%20an%20apparent%20dig%20at%20the%20opposition%2C%20which%20has%20used%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20issue%20to%20target%20the%20group%20and%20the%20government%20on%20several%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20also%20asked%20whether%20these%20people%20and%20entities%20knew%20about%20the%20Chinese%20link.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Misrepresentations'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%2C%20in%20its%20show%20cause%20notice%20to%20Hindenburg%20Research%20LLC%20said%20the%20organisation's%20report%20contained%20misrepresentations%20and%20inaccurate%20statements%20which%20built%20a%20convenient%20narrative%20through%20selective%20disclosures%20and%20catchy%20headlines%20to%20cause%20panic%20in%20Adani%20share%20prices%2C%20thereby%20deflating%20the%20prices%20of%20the%20Adani%20group%20stocks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindenburg%20has%20claimed%20that%20it%20did%20not%20provide%20research%20notice%20to%20Kingdon%20before%20sharing%20the%20draft%20report%20and%20Kingdon%20did%20not%20share%20the%20trading%20notice%20with%20Hindenburg%20before%20the%20report%20was%20shared%20publicly%20through%20mass%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20International%20Ltd%20spokesperson%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20KMIL%20and%20KIOF%20%26quot%3Bunequivocally%20state%20that%20Hindenburg%20has%20never%20been%20a%20client%20of%20the%20firm%20nor%20has%20it%20ever%20been%20an%20investor%20in%20the%20Fund.%20The%20Fund%20was%20never%20aware%20that%20Hindenburg%20was%20a%20partner%20of%20any%20of%20its%20investors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKMIL%20has%20also%20received%20a%20confirmation%20and%20declaration%20from%20the%20Fund's%20investor%20that%20its%20investments%20were%20made%20as%20a%20principal%20and%20not%20on%20behalf%20of%20any%20other%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720111620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-07%2F2rnf431_adani-logo-reuters-generic-650_625x300_20_July_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindenburg-adani-group-anla-cheng-senior-lawyer-points-to-china-link-in-hindenburgs-attack-on-adani-group-6035299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20stunning%20claim%20that%20he%20has%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmoking%20gun%26quot%3B%2C%20senior%20lawyer%20Mahesh%20Jethmalani%20has%20alleged%20that%20a%20businessman%20with%20Chinese%20links%20had%20commissioned%20the%20report%20by%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindenburg-adani-group-anla-cheng-senior-lawyer-points-to-china-link-in-hindenburgs-attack-on-adani-group-6035299%22%2C%22cdnAm