ith%20The%20Bay%20Area's%20crime%20and%20wanted%20a%20family-friendly%20and%20lively%20city.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESince%20moving%2C%20Liaw%20said%20it's%20his%20mission%20to%20introduce%20others%20to%20everything%20Vegas%20has%20to%20offer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Teddy%20Liaw%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20CEO%20of%20contact%20center%20solutions%20company%20NexRep%2C%20who%20moved%20from%20San%20Francisco%20to%20Summerlin%2C%20Nevada%2C%20a%20Las%20Vegas%20suburb%2C%20in%202021%20after%20he%20grew%20frustrated%20by%20crime%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area.%20Liaw%20founded%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vegastechsummit.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EVegas%20Tech%20Summit%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20multi-day%20tech%20conference%20promoting%20Vegas%20as%20a%20burgeoning%20tech%20center.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20absolutely%20loved%20the%20Bay%20Area.%20I%20loved%20the%20culture%2C%20the%20food%2C%20the%20people%2C%20the%20intellect%2C%20and%20the%20gorgeous%20views%20of%20the%20water%20surrounding%20an%20amazing%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20COVID-19%20absolutely%20wrecked%20the%20city.%20It's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsan-francisco-pain-worsens-workers-visitors-shoppers-leave-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20the%20same%20San%20Francisco%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20before.%20It's%20still%20rebounding%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20all%20the%20way%20back%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20been%20living%20in%20San%20Francisco%20for%20about%2015%20years%20before%20I%20moved.%20I%20owned%20a%20condo%20that%20had%20a%20gorgeous%20bay%20view%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-remote-jobs-community-santa-cruz-sacramento-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBay%20Area%20had%20so%20much%20to%20offer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20a%20thriving%20entrepreneurial%20and%20tech%20ecosystem%20that%20made%20very%20smart%20people%20smarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20there%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-san-francisco-crime-drugs-homelessness-politics-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erampant%20crime%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20don't%20appreciate%20it%20when%20people%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20homelessness%20issue%20because%20San%20Francisco%20has%20had%20homeless%20people%20before%20and%20found%20ways%20to%20provide%20services.%20That%20was%20the%20narrative%20during%20COVID.%20But%20it's%20not%20a%20homelessness%20issue.%20It%20was%20a%20safety%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%202020%2C%20my%20house%20was%20burglarized.%20My%20experience%20with%20law%20enforcement%20was%20not%20positive.%20That%20was%20the%20last%20straw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20got%20two%20young%20kids%2C%20and%20I%20asked%20myself%3A%20Is%20this%20the%20type%20of%20environment%20that%20will%20be%20safe%20for%20my%20family%3F%20The%20answer%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20was%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2291a2af81-5264-4c07-935e-6847c25c4a07%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEverywhere%20was%20on%20the%20table%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20considering%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Washington%20State%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-california-austin-texas-10-things-i-wish-i-knew-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETexas%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202021%2C%20right%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20COVID%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-las-vegas-from-california-weather-living-cost-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escouting%20trip%20to%20Vegas%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20what%20Vegas%20had%20to%20offer%2C%20including%20new%20houses%2C%20clean%20living%2C%20and%20ample%20playgrounds%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20amazing%20food%20of%20all%20ethnicities%2C%20cuisines%2C%20and%20cultures.%20Vegas%20has%20entertainment%2C%20family%20life%2C%20and%20suburbia%20life%2C%20just%2020%20minutes%20away%20from%20all%20the%20socializing%20you%20would%20ever%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20a%20very%20easy%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20Summerlin%2C%20Nevada%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6685be291aace5b3ada46d8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESummerlin%20is%20a%20suburb%20about%2020%20minutes%20outside%20Las%20Vegas.%3Cp%3Ehalbergman%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESummerlin%20is%20a%20master-planned%20community%20about%2020%20minutes%20from%20all%20the%20action.%20You%20can't%20go%20more%20than%20half%20a%20mile%20without%20running%20into%20a%20park.%20We're%20in%20a%20desert%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20greenery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESummerlin%20is%20designed%20for%20families.%20It%20has%20an%20amazing%20list%20of%20school%20options%20from%20preschool%20through%20high%20school%2C%20including%20some%20of%20the%20top%20private%20schools%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20I%20like%20to%20play%20golf%2C%20and%20there%20are%20so%20many%20golf%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20close%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-pay-cut-moved-california-las-vegas-happy-remote-work-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E7%2C000%20square%20feet%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20two%20swimming%20pools%20here%20for%20the%20same%20price%20as%20I%20got%20my%20four-bedroom%20condo%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area.%20I%20needed%20a%20house%20that%20my%20friends%20wanted%20to%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20I%20moved%2C%20I%20started%20invi