an-virginia-mccullough-pleads-guilty-murdering-parents-family-home-essex%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Dave%20Oldershaw%2C%20a%20neighbour%2C%20said%20McCullough%20was%20%26quot%3Bcarrying%20on%2C%20going%20up%20to%20the%20Chinese%20(takeaway)%20like%20nothing%20has%20happened%26quot%3B.%20He%20%26quot%3Bthought%20she%20lived%20on%20her%20own%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20house%20and%20stated%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bonly%20knew%20her%20to%20say%20hello%20to%20-%20she%20wasn't%20trouble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20worker%20at%20a%20nearby%20shop%20said%20the%20woman%20had%20told%20him%20her%20parents%20had%20moved%20to%20be%20by%20the%20seaside.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20not%20seen%20them%20since%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20but%20would%20previously%20%26quot%3Bsee%20them%20two%20or%20three%20times%20per%20week%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20employee%2C%20McCullough%20appeared%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20bit%20odd%20sometimes.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BShe%20would%20come%20in%20and%20go%20'do%20you%20want%20a%20coffee'%20then%20five%20minutes%20later%2C%20there%20would%20be%20a%20coffee%20sitting%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20worker%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720108260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fk2l02g1o_earplifting_625x300_04_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-murdered-parents-lived-with-their-dead-bodies-for-several-years-6034977%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20woman%20lied%20to%20the%20doctors%20and%20relatives%20that%20her%20parents%20were%20unwell%2C%20on%20holiday%20or%20on%20vacation%20to%20cover%20her%20tracks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-murdered-parents-lived-with-their-dead-bodies-for-several-years-6034977%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-murdered-parents-lived-with-their-dead-bodies-for-several-years-6034977%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-murdered-parents-lived-with-their-dead-bodies-for-several-years-6034977%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stolen%20campaign%20poster%3F%20Hidden%20AirTags%20are%20the%20new%20defense.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223942%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holding%20an%20Apple%20AirTag%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6686a0fe268f62ba18a78aef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221971%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOver%20thirty%20plaintiffs%20have%20joined%20a%20class%20action%20lawsuit%20that%20Apple%20AirTags%20helped%20facilitate%20stalking.%3Cp%3EMelina%20Mara%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPeople%20are%20hiding%20AirTags%20in%20campaign%20posters%20to%20stop%20thieves%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reports.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tracking%20devices%20are%20helping%20recover%20signs%20and%20charge%20those%20who%20took%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20those%20charged%20included%20political%20opponents%2C%20WSJ%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20political%20tale%20as%20old%20as%20time%3A%20put%20up%20a%20campaign%20poster%20in%20your%20yard%2C%20and%20thieves%20come%20to%20snatch%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcampaign-signs-stolen-apple-airtag-tracking-e7d17efb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20those%20fed%20up%20with%20front%20lawn%20looting%20are%20embracing%20a%20modern%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20geo-tracking%20AirTag%20devices%20are%20helping%20owners%20find%20their%20signs%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sometimes%2C%20even%20the%20people%20who%20stole%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20practice%20has%20already%20led%20to%20charges.%20In%20one%20example%20cited%20by%20the%20outlet%2C%20Florida%20politician%20John%20Dittmore%20decided%20to%20hide%20the%20coin-sized%20gadget%20on%20one%20of%20his%20posters%20after%20waking%20up%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fox35orlando.com%2Fnews%2Fthefts-campaign-signs-under-investigation-brevard-county%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enumber%20of%20thefts%20in%20May%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20sign%20was%20taken%20overnight%2C%20the%20Brevard%20County%20Commission%20candidate%20tracked%20the%20AirTag's%20pings%20to%20a%20pickup%20truck%20eight%20miles%20away.%20Police%20questioned%20two%20teens%2C%20and%20they%20were%20charged%20with%20criminal%20mischief%20and%20the%20theft%20of%20nine%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncluding%20the%20poster%20stands%20that%20were%20also%20taken%2C%20the%20stolen%20property%20had%20a%20total%20value%20of%20over%20%241%2C100%2C%20WSJ%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20cited%20cases%2C%20stolen%20signs%20don't%20end%20up%20with%20teens%2C%20but%20in%20the%20homes%20of%20electoral%20opponents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Chris%20Torre%20became%20the%20victim%20of%20poster%20snatching%2C%20AirTags%20led%20him%20to%20the%20residence%20of%20Renee%20Rountree%2C%20the%20Journal%20said.%20Both%20were%20running%20for%20a%20seat%20on%20the%20Isle%20of%20Wight%20County%20Board%20of%20Supervisors%20in%20Virginia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20son-in-law%20was%20charged%20with%20a%20misdemeanor%20for%20stealing%20the%20property%2C%20while%20Rountree%20faced%20a%20misdemeanor%20for%20receiving%20stolen%20goods.%20In%20a%20December%20trial%2C%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.13newsnow.com%2Farticle%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fisle-of-wight-county%2Fisle-of-wight-elected-official-ordered-250-hours-community-service-hiding-opponents-stolen-campaign-signs%2F291-6c3faba3-134b-4a87-a582-ae2a954b712d%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enoted%20plans%20to%20return%20the%20signs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Rountree%20has%20since%20been%20ordered%20to%20250%20hours%20of%20community%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20think%20that%20this%20will%20have%20a%20huge%20deterrent%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20trial's%20judge%20said%20in%20the%20court's%20transcript%2C%20quoted%20by%20WSJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20judge%20was%20speaking%20of%20Rountree%2C%20the%20point%20outlines%20another%20big%20appeal%20of%20AirTags%3A%20if%20thieves%20know%20to%20suspect%20that%20a%20device%20might%20be%20planted%20on%20a%20poster%2C%20they%20might%20be%20less%20inclined%20to%20take%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lot%20like%20when%20cops%20mark%20themselves%20on%20Waze%2C%26quot%3B%20New%20Jersey%20deputy%20mayor%20Vinny%20Panico%2C%20who%20tracked%20a%20lost%20poster%20to%20a%20local%20committeeman's%20house%2C%20told%20the%20outlet%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20that%20slows%20people%20down%2C%20that%20slows%20people%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20AirTags%20don't%20solve%20everything.%20Lawn%20posters%20are%20still%20exposed%20to%20destruction%2C%20with%20some%20vandals%20going%20as%20far%20as%20to%20drive%20over%20signs%20they%20don't%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20technology's%20capabilities%20have%20recouped%20more%20than%20just%20lawn%20signs.%20These%20devices%20keep%20track%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fapple-airtag-for-wallet-luggage-moving%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elost%20wallets%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-airtags-helped-me-find-my-lost-suitcase-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eairline%20baggage%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassengers-beg-airlines-to-look-at-apple-airtags-to-find-lost-luggage-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eairline%20itself%20can't%20find%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20or%20let%20parents%20keep%20tabs%20on%20their%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20criticism%20has%20also%20mounted%20against%20the%20%2429%20geo-trackers%2C%20over%20fears%20that%20they%20provide%20a%20cheap%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-airtag-dozens-more-stalking-victims-join-lawsuit-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etool%20for%20stalkers%20or%20abusers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20lawsuit%20against%20Apple%20was%20filed%20in%202022%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20March%2C%20a%20judge%20denied%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fapple-airtags-stalking-lawsuits-e59166988920c4ba1e82956ea85c1677%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirm's%20motion%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-airtags-local-elections-politics-campaign-poster-sign-tracking-device-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720108260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6617ba133f923f7dab06afc1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-airtags-local-elections-politics-campaign-poster-sign-tracking-device-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Politicians%20are%20fighting%20back%20against%20sign%20snatching%20with%20AirTags%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-airtags-local-elections-politics-campaign-poster-sign-tracking-device-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Terrorist%20Planning%20Lone%20Wolf%20Attack%20Arrested%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3A%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20breakthrough%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Anti-Terrorism%20Squad%20(ATS)%20has%20arrested%20an%20alleged%20Indian%20Mujahideen%20terrorist%20who%20was%20planning%20a%20lone%20wolf%20attack%20on%20personnel%20from%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20officials%20said%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaizan%20Sheikh%2C%2034%2C%20was%20arrested%20from%20Kanhar%20Mohalla%20in%20Khandwa's%20Saluja%20colony%20after%20a%20raid%20on%20his%20residence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20raid%2C%20ATS%20officers%20seized%20a%20substantial%20amount%20of%20jihadi%20literature%20related%20to%20the%20Indian%20Mujahideen%20(IM)%2C%20ISIS%2C%20and%20other%20terrorist%20organisations.%20They%20also%20recovered%20a%20pistol%2C%20five%20live%20cartridges%2C%20four%20mobile%20phones%20and%20membership%20forms%20for%20the%20banned%20organisation%20Student's%20Islamic%20Movement%20of%20India%20(SIMI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20seized%20mobile%20phones%20and%20digital%20devices%20contained%20jihadi%20literature%2C%20videos%2C%20and%20photos%20from%20various%20terrorist%20organisations%2C%20including%20IM%2C%20Jaish-e-Mohammed%20and%20Lashkar-e-Taiba.%20Faizan%20was%20also%20found%20to%20be%20in%20contact%20with%20members%20of%20SIMI%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Faizan%20had%20been%20using%20social%20media%2C%20particularly%20Facebook%20ID%2C%20to%20propagate%20the%20ideologies%20of%20IM%20and%20ISIS.%20The%2034-year-old%20circulated%20videos%20from%20Mujahideen%20training%20camps%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20speeches%20by%20Jaish-e-Mohammed%20chief%20Masood%20Azhar%20and%20terrorists%20from%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%2C%20details%20about%20the%20Kandahar%20plane%20hijacking%2C%20statements%20by%20Mullah%20Omar%2C%20and%20posts%20related%20to%20Ansar%20Ghazwat-ul-Hind%20(AGH).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFaizan%20had%20been%20meticulously%20planning%20a%20lone%20wolf%20attack%2C%20monitoring%20and%20tracking%20the%20movements%20of%20security%20force%20personnel%20and%20their%20families.%20His%20objective%20was%20to%20emulate%20terrorists%20like%20Yasin%20Bhatkal%20of%20Indian%20Mujahideen%20and%20SIMI%20chief%20Abul%20Fazal%2C%20aspiring%20to%20gain%20recognition.%20To%20execute%20his%20plan%2C%20Faizan%20was%20also%20in%20the%20process%20of%20acquiring%20more%20pistols%20and%20cartridges%20through%20connections%20with%20local%20illegal%20arms%20dealers%20and%20individuals%20from%20outside%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EATS%20Inspector%20General%20Dr%20Ashish%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20leadership%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Dr%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20the%20state%20has%20adopted%20a%20zero-tolerance%20policy%20towards%20terrorism%20and%20anti-national%20activities.%20The%20arrest%20is%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20effort%20to%20maintain%20heightened%20surveillance%20across%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaizan%20has%20been%20charged%20under%20sections%20of%20the%20stringent%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201967.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20has%20taken%20Faizan%20on%20remand%20for%20interrogation%2C%20aiming%20to%20uncover%20information%20about%20his%20associates%20and%20details%20of%20his%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20ATS%20has%20successfully%20arrested%2022%20people%20associated%20with%20the%20Popular%20Front%20of%20India%2C%20six%20with%20ISIS%2C%20six%20with%20Jamaat-ul-Mujahideen%20Bangladesh%20(JMB)%2C%2016%20with%20Hizb-ut-Tahrir%20(HuT)%2C%20and%2055%20other%20suspected%20terrorists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20has%20also%20seized%20a%20substantial%20quantity%20of%20arms%2C%20ammunition%2C%20anti-national%20literature%2C%20objectionable%20documents%2C%20and%20digital%20equipment%20from%20these%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%202005%20and%202013%2C%20IM%20was%20involved%20in%20multiple%20bomb%20blasts%20across%20India%2C%20including%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20and%20Pune.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20IM%20co-founder%20Riyaz%20Bhatkal%20has%20established%20a%20robust%20network%20of%20members%2C%20focusing%20on%20recruitment%20and%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720108200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fst18jaj8_terrorist-arrested-khandwa_625x300_04_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorist-planning-lone-wolf-attack-on-security-personnel-arrested-in-madhya-pradesh-cops-6034787%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20significant%20breakthrough%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Anti-Terrorism%20Squad%20(ATS)%20has%20arrested%20an%20alleged%20Indian%20Mujahideen%20terrorist%20who%20was%20planning%20a%20lone%20wolf%20attack%20on%20personnel%20from%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20officials%20said%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorist-planning-lone-wolf-attack-on-security-personnel-arrested-in-madhya-pradesh-cops-6034787%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorist-planning-lone-wolf-attack-on-security-personnel-arrested-in-madhya-pradesh-cops-6034787%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorist-planning-lone-wolf-attack-on-security-personnel-arrested-in-madhya-pradesh-cops-6034787%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Germany%20summons%20Turkish%20ambassador%20as%20row%20over%20Euros%20wolf%20salute%20grows%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720107960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F07%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-merih-demiral-arda-guler_6597427.jpg%3F20240703124712%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Feuro-2024-germany-summons-turkish-ambassador-as-row-over-wolf-salute-grows-13163692%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Germany%20has%20summoned%20Turkey's%20ambassador%20as%20the%20row%20over%20a%20Turkish%20player's%20ultra-nationalist%20gesture%20at%20Euro%202024%20gr