caption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f21daaa5-fe4f-4ee6-aca8-b232ebb1480a%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20build%20a%20viral%20app%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Noplace%20had%20nearly%20half%20a%20million%20users%20on%20its%20waitlist%20just%20last%20month%2C%20the%20app%20has%20been%20testing%20for%20much%20longer%20and%20it%20even%20had%20a%20different%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhong%20started%20testing%20the%20app%2C%20then%20called%20Nospace%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-social-media-apps-worth-downloading-recommendations-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20late-2023%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20smaller%20number%20of%20users%20who%20would%20need%20to%20wait%20and%20receive%20invite%20codes%20to%20access%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20started%20doing%20wait%20lists%2C%20it%20was%20really%20a%20way%20for%20people%20to%20reserve%20your%20username%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhong%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20people%20to%20feel%20excited%20and%20early.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20small%20team%20of%20seven%20continued%20to%20test%20the%20app%20in%20a%20closed%20setting%2C%20which%20allowed%20them%20to%20iterate%20fast%2C%20remove%20unnecessary%20features%2C%20navigate%20trust%20and%20safety%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20down%20on%20the%20things%20that%20are%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhong%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20the%20app%20was%20gaining%20popularity%2C%20in%20April%2C%20Zhong%20was%20sent%20a%20cease%20and%20desist%20letter%20from%20another%20company.%20Zhong%20declined%20to%20name%20the%20company%2C%20but%20one%20can%20speculate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Nospace%20changed%20its%20name.%20It%20also%20capitalized%20on%20the%20drama%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ft%2FZPREQ4xQA%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturned%20to%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20hype%20up%20the%20renaming%20process.%20Zhong%20said%20they%20received%20thousands%20of%20submissions%20unt