ctions%2C%20Noplace%20feels%20timely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhong%20compared%20her%20app%20to%20incumbents%20like%20Twitter%2C%20TikTok%2C%20and%20even%20Reddit%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20not%20oriented%20toward%20community%20and%20it's%20more%20so%20just%20consuming%20content%20and%20media.%20Reddit%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%A6%20it's%20really%20good%20for%20information.%20I%20use%20it%20for%20information%2C%20not%20for%20connecting%20with%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReddit%20is%20an%20important%20source%20of%20inspiration%20for%20Zhong's%20app%20as%20well%2C%20since%20one%20of%20Reddit's%20founders%2C%20Alexis%20Ohanian%2C%20has%20advised%20Zhong%20on%20her%20app%20and%20his%20firm%20776%20invested%20in%20her%20previous%20company%2C%20Islands%20XYZ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20seen%20how%20this%20company%20has%20changed%20over%20time%2C%20but%20this%20is%20also%20very%20aligned%20with%20his%20experience%20at%20Reddit%2C%20and%20it's%20been%20very%20helpful%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhong%20said.%20Like%20Reddit%2C%20pseudonyms%20are%20very%20common%20and%20part%20of%20the%20experience%20on%20Noplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Zhong%20looks%20ahead%2C%20however%2C%20she's%20wary%20of%20following%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20social%20media%20giants%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20scaling%20the%20app%20and%20adding%20more%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20be%20very%20thoughtful%20about%20not%20bloating%20the%20app%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20kind%20of%20the%20downfall%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20social%20apps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Noplace%20plans%20to%20expand%20its%20group%20chat%20features%20with%20AI%20tools%20that%20can%20help%20bolster%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20staying%20relevant%2C%20Zhong%20knows%2C%20will%20be%20the%20next%20test%20for%20Noplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20risk%20being%20a%20fad%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%2C%20social%20apps%20