C%20I%20was%20taught%20the%20nitty%20gritty%20of%20pearl%20farming.%20I%20learnt%20how%20to%20source%20raw%20material%2C%20how%20to%20nucleate%20mussels%2C%20what%20food%20to%20offer%20the%20mussels%20and%20their%20surgical%20procedure%2C%20and%20how%20to%20make%20both%20designer%20pearls%20and%20round%20pearls.%20With%20this%20training%2C%20which%20cost%20me%20Rs%208%2C000%2C%20I%20became%20confident%20about%20implementing%20it%20on%20the%20ground.%20I%20also%20received%20the%20certification%20to%20practise%20pearl%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20September%202022%2C%20Gaurav%20prepared%20a%20pond%20of%20150%20x%2080%20feet%20in%20his%20village%20in%20Bharatpur%20district%20and%20added%201.15%20lakh%20mussels%20to%20the%20pond.%20Interestingly%2C%20he%20roped%20in%20other%20small%20farmers%20in%20the%20projects%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20thought%20of%20starting%20pearl%20farming%20at%20a%20small%20scale%20but%20as%20and%20when%20I%20discussed%20this%20with%20more%20and%20more%20farmers%2C%20they%20became%20interested%20in%20investing%20in%20the%20work.%20Of%201.15%20lakh%20mussels%2C%20I%20had%20invested%20in%2050%2C000%20mussels%20personally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaurav%20started%20the%20project%20by%20investing%20Rs%2021%20lakh%2C%20of%20which%20Rs%208%20lakh%20was%20spent%20on%20establishing%20the%20pond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-2-1719841114.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gaurav%20attended%20a%20five-day%20training%20at%20the%20Central%20Institute%20for%20Freshwater%20Aquaculture%20(CIFA)%20in%20Odisha.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-2-1719841114.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-2-1719841114-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-2-1719841114-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-2-1719841114-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-2-1719841114-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355092%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGaurav%20attended%20a%20five-day%20training%20at%20the%20Central%20Institute%20for%20Freshwater%20Aquaculture%20(CIFA)%20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20nucleating%20mussels%2C%20we%20put%20them%20in%20small%20nets%20and%20transferred%20them%20into%20the%20pond.%20This%20process%20took%20us%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half.%20But%20the%20work%20was%20not%20yet%20finished.%20We%20had%20to%20maintain%20the%20pond%20thereafter.%20Every%20month%2C%20we%20added%20feed%20and%20maintained%20oxygen%20in%20the%20pond%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20mussels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%2021%20months%20of%20patiently%20waiting%20for%20the%20mussels%20to%20turn%20into%20pearls%2C%20Gaurav%20finally%20got%20the%20results.%20%E2%80%9COur%20happiness%20knew%20no%20bounds.%20We%20fetched%20Rs%20110%20per%20pearl%20and%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%201.25%20crore%20and%20made%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%2080%20lakh.%20To%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20this%20profit%20in%20a%201.5%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%20land%20is%20a%20big%20deal%20for%20us.%20Farmers%20in%20200%20villages%20collectively%20could%20not%20earn%20this%20much%20by%20growing%20wheat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPersonally%2C%20I%20earned%20Rs%2055%20lakh%20after%20investing%20Rs%2021%20lakh.%20This%20was%202.5%20times%20earnings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20beams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20feat%20was%20not%20as%20easy.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20challenges%20in%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20is%20managing%20weather%20conditions.%20Rajasthan%20has%20very%20warm%20weather%20and%20it%20took%20two%20days%20of%20travel%20by%20train%20to%20source%20mussels%20from%20Odisha.%20In%20this%20process%2C%20the%20mussels%20became%20very%20weak%20as%20they%20were%20without%20water%20for%20so%20long%2C%20which%20increased%20the%20mortality%20rate%20to%2050%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20start%20pearl%20farming%20in%20the%20extreme%20winters%20of%20January%20instead%20of%20September%20and%20October%20when%20the%20weather%20is%20still%20hot%20in%20Rajasthan.%20In%20early%202023%2C%20when%20I%20procured%20mussels%2C%20the%20mortality%20rate%20was%20just%2030%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl_11zon-1719841237.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gaurav%20along%20with%20other%20farmers%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%201.25%20crore.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl_11zon-1719841237.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl_11zon-1719841237-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl_11zon-1719841237-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl_11zon-1719841237-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl_11zon-1719841237-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355096%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGaurav%20along%20with%20other%20farmers%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%20over%201.25%20crore.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20matter%20how%20many%20books%20I%20read%20or%20videos%20I%20watched%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20would%20not%20learn%20anything%20unless%20I%20experimented%20on%20the%20ground.%20I%20understood%20the%20challenges%20and%20then%20worked%20on%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20waiting%20for%20the%20results%20of%20the%20first%20batch%2C%20Gaurav%20also%20started%20working%20on%20the%20second%20batch%20simultaneously%20and%20established%20another%20pond.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20interrupted%20and%20taunted%20me%20for%20this%20decision.%20They%20asked%20why%20I%20was%20willing%20to%20invest%20and%20potentially%20waste%20more%20money%20even%20before%20receiving%20any%20income%20from%20the%20first%20batch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20takes%20around%2021%20months%20to%20prepare%20one%20batch%2C%20which%20is%20a%20time-consuming%20process.%20So%20he%20was%20prepared%20to%20be%20patient%20and%20hopeful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20replied%20back%20to%20any%20taunts%20but%20patiently%20waited%20for%20the%20results.%20And%2021%20months%20later%2C%20we%20earned%20Rs%201.25%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20Today%2C%20Gaurav%20has%20expanded%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20in%20three%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342922%2Fhow-to-do-pearl-farming-in-artificial-ponds-in-rajasthan-computer-teacher-reaps-huge-profits%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eponds%20in%20Rajasthan%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20two%20ponds%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20to%20earn%20an%20income%20for%20myself%20but%20this%20has%20also%20helped%20me%20establish%20an%20identity%20by%20doing%20unique%20work.%20Besides%2C%20this%20work%20has%20become%20an%20income%20source%20for%20other%20small%20farmers%20who%20invested%20in%20this%20project.%20It%20was%20better%20than%20investing%20in%20mutual%20funds%20or%20fixed%20deposits.%20It%20was%20so%20fulfilling%20to%20see%20the%20results%20because%20it%20shaped%20my%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Gaurav%20Pachauri.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719845248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gaurav%20Pachauri%20took%20up%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20after%20failing%20to%20crack%20government%20exams%20for%20four%20years.%20He%20set%20up%20a%20pearl%20farm%20in%20Bharatpur%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20earning%20Rs%2055%20lakh%20within%2021%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355072%2Ffreshwater-pearl-farming-help-local-farmers-earn-lakhs-gaurav-pachauri-bharatpur-rajasthan%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ladakhi%20Aerospace%20Engineer%E2%80%99s%20Research%20in%20Europe%20Could%20Pave%20the%20Way%20for%20Silent%20Aeroplanes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20things%20mobility%2C%20the%20future%20of%20air%20transport%20is%20also%20electric.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20push%20by%20the%20aviation%20industry%20to%20decarbonise%20air%20transport%20given%20the%20myriad%20ways%20it%20pollutes%20the%20environment%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311459%2Fpad-care-labs-safe-disposal-of-sanitary-pads-cuts-carbon-converts-into-packaging-ajinkya-dhariya%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarbon%20emissions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20noise%20pollution.%20%3Cem%3E(Image%20above%20of%20Dr%20Feroz%20Ahmed%2C%20aerospace%20engineer)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20you%20have%20eVTOLs%20(electric%20Vertical%20Take-Off%20and%20Landing%20aircraft)%2C%20sometimes%20referred%20to%20as%20air%20taxis%20or%20flying%20taxis%2C%20like%20the%20Lilium%20Jet%20%E2%80%94%20a%20prototype%20eVTOL%20designed%20by%20Lilium%20GmbH%2C%20a%20German%20aerospace%20company.%20Unlike%20conventional%20aeroplanes%2C%20eVTOLs%20fly%20like%20helicopters%20and%20typically%20carry%20anywhere%20between%20two%20to%20six%20passengers%2C%20including%20a%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20eVTOLs%2C%20there%20are%20aircrafts%20like%20the%20E9X%20%E2%80%94%20a%20prototype%20electric%20aircraft%20designed%20by%20Dutch%20aviation%20startup%20Elysian%2C%20which%20they%20claim%20can%20hold%2090%20passengers%20and%20fly%20up%20to%20500%20miles%20without%20having%20to%20stop%20to%20recharge.%20According%20to%20ABC%20News%2C%20E9X%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20service%20by%202033.%20There%20is%20also%20the%20NOVA%20developed%20by%20ONERA%2C%20the%20French%20national%20aerospace%20research%20centre%2C%20which%20they%20claim%20is%20designed%20to%20carry%20180%20passengers%20on%203%2C000%20nautical%20miles%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20service%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLilium_EBACE_2023_Le_Grand-Saconnex_EB237483-1719838871.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerospace%20engineer%20developing%20silent%20aeroplanes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLilium_EBACE_2023_Le_Grand-Saconnex_EB237483-1719838871.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLilium_EBACE_2023_Le_Grand-Saconnex_EB237483-1719838871-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLilium_EBACE_2023_Le_Grand-Saconnex_EB237483-1719838871-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLilium_EBACE_2023_Le_Grand-Saconnex_EB237483-1719838871-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLilium_EBACE_2023_Le_Grand-Saconnex_EB237483-1719838871-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355043%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELilium%20static%20demonstrator%20at%20EBACE%202023%20at%20Palexpo%2C%20Le%20Grand-Saconnex%20(Image%20courtesy%20Wikimedia%20Commons)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuffice%20it%20to%20say%2C%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20demand%20for%20these%20modern%20urban%20air%20mobility%20(UAM)%20systems%20that%20aim%20to%20offer%20a%20pleasant%20flight%20experience%20while%20minimising%20carbon%20footprint.%20Regulatory%20and%20governing%20bodies%20around%20the%20world%20like%20the%20European%20Commission%20have%20taken%20note%20of%20this%20demand.%20In%20its%20Flight%20Path%202050%20(FP250)%20challenge%2C%20the%20European%20Commission%20has%20set%20ambitious%20targets%20for%20future%20commercial%20transport%20aircraft%2C%20including%20a%20reduction%20of%20CO2%20emissions%20by%2075%25%2C%20NOx%20emissions%20by%2095%25%2C%20and%20noise%20emissions%20by%2065%25%20by%20the%20year%202050.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20modern%20UAM%20systems%20address%20carbon%20emissions%20with%20reliance%20on%20electric%20batteries%20rather%20than%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20the%20challenge%20of%20nose%20emission%20remains%20unresolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Dr%20Feroz%20Ahmed%2C%20a%20Ladakhi%20aerospace%20engineer%20and%20Senior%20Research%20Associate%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Bristol%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20electric%20engines%20are%20generally%20quieter%20than%20their%20combustion%20counterparts%2C%20the%20overall%20noise%20levels%20of%20UAM%20systems%20can%20still%20be%20significant%20due%20to%20factors%20like%20rotor%2Ffan%2Fpropeller%20noise%20and%20the%20frequency%20of%20operations%20near%20populated%20areas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20challenge%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F193055%2Fmumbai-woman-fighting-noise-pollution-silent-zone-freedom-struggle-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enoise%20pollution%3C%2Fa%3E%20remains%20significant%2C%20as%20it%20impacts%20community%20health%2C%20disrupts%20wildlife%2C%20and%20is%20critical%20for%20gaining%20regulatory%20and%20public%20acceptance.%20Therefore%2C%20despite%20advancements%20in%20emission%20reductions%2C%20the%20aviation%20industry%20must%20also%20prioritise%20developing%20technologies%20to%20reduce%20noise%20levels%20to%20ensure%20the%20broader%20acceptance%20and%20success%20of%20new%20aircraft%20technologies%2C%20including%20modern%20UAM%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2035-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20970px)%20100vw%2C%20970px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flarge-passenger-jet-flying-through-blue-sky-1719840175.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22970%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22aerospace%20engineer%20doing%20groundbreaking%20research%20on%20silent%20aeroplanes%20and%20flights%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flarge-passenger-jet-flying-through-blue-sky-1719840175.jpg%20970w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flarge-passenger-jet-flying-through-blue-sky-1719840175-300x185.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flarge-passenger-jet-flying-through-blue-sky-1719840175-500x308.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flarge-passenger-jet-flying-through-blue-sky-1719840175-768x473.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flarge-passenger-jet-flying-through-blue-sky-1719840175-150x92.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355070%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22597%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20representational%20purposes%20only%3A%20Conventional%20air%20travel%20pollutes%20the%20environment%20(Image%20courtesy%20Freerange%20Stock)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20noise%20pollution%20in%20aviation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConventional%20commercial%20aeroplanes%20are%20quite%20noisy%20mainly%20because%20of%20two%20types%20of%20noise%20from%20their%20engines%3A%20mechanical%20noise%20and%20aerodynamic%20noise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMechanical%20noise%20comes%20from%20moving%20parts%20inside%20the%20engine%2C%20such%20as%20gears%2C%20rotors%2C%20turbines%2C%20and%20combustion%20chambers.%20This%20noise%20also%20includes%20sounds%20from%20imbalances%20when%20these%20parts%20don%E2%80%99t%20spin%20perfectly%2C%20causing%20vibrations.%20Aerodynamic%20noise%20is%20created%20because%20of%20how%20the%20air%20moves%20around%20and%20through%20the%20engine.%20As%20the%20engine%E2%80%99s%20fan%20blades%20spin%20rapidly%2C%20they%20chop%20through%20the%20air%2C%20which%20can%20be%20noisy.%20Plus%2C%20when%20air%20rushes%20over%20the%20engine%E2%80%99s%20surfaces%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20aeroplane%20at%20high%20speeds%2C%20it%20generates%20even%20more%20noise%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20loud%20whoosh%20you%20hear%20when%20you%20stick%20your%20hand%20out%20of%20a%20moving%20car%20window%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Ahmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20in%20future%20electric%20aeroplanes%2C%20mechanical%20noise%20will%20be%20significantly%20reduced%20because%20these%20aircrafts%20will%20rely%20on%20electric%20motors%2C%20which%20have%20fewer%20moving%20parts%20like%20gears%2C%20rotors%2C%20and%20turbines.%20This%20means%20there%20will%20be%20less%20vibration%20and%20fewer%20sources%20of%20imbalance-related%20noise.%20But%20aerodynamic%20noise%20will%20still%20be%20present%2C%20as%20the%20movement%20of%20air%20around%20the%20aircraft%20and%20through%20any%20fans%20or%20propellers%20used%20to%20generate%20lift%20and%20propulsion%20will%20continue%20to%20create%20noise%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%20in%20April%2C%20Dr%20Feroz%20Ahmed%20and%20his%20team%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Bristol%E2%80%99s%20School%20of%20Civil%2C%20Aerospace%20and%20Design%20Engineering%2C%20published%20a%20breakthrough%20study%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Fluid%20Mechanics%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fjournals%2Fjournal-of-fluid-mechanics%2Farticle%2Faeroacoustics-of-a-ducted-fan-ingesting-an-adverse-pressure-gradient-boundary-layer%2F2BCCFB29FE97AF669CE586DE51C27BDA%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20%E2%80%9Creveals%20for%20the%20first%20time%E2%80%9D%20how%20noise%20is%20generated%20and%20propagated%20from%20boundary%20layer%20ingesting%20(BLI)%20ducted%20fans%20featuring%20in%20modern%20electric%20UAM%20systems%2C%20thus%20possibly%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20future%20of%20silent%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CBLI%20ducted%20fans%2C%20also%20known%20as%20embedded%20engines%2C%20are%20similar%20to%20large%20engines%20found%20in%20modern%20aeroplanes%20but%20are%20partially%20embedded%20into%20the%20plane%E2%80%99s%20main%20body%20instead%20of%20under%20the%20wings%20far%20from%20the%20main%20body.%20As%20they%20ingest%20air%20from%20both%20the%20front%20and%20from%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20airframe%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20work%20as%20hard%20to%20move%20the%20plane%2C%20so%20it%20burns%20less%20fuel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriting%20for%20Aerospace%20Testing%20International%2C%20Dr%20Ahmed%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CElectric%20ducted%20fan%20propulsion%20systems%20are%20gaining%20significant%20attention%20for%20their%20potential%20to%20help%20power%20next-generation%20aircraft%20toward%20Net%20Zero%20emissions.%20These%20systems%20are%20typically%20mounted%20in%20two%20ways%2C%20away%20from%20the%20airframe%2C%20or%20close%20to%20or%20embedded%20within%20the%20airframe.%20The%20latter%20are%20known%20as%20boundary%20layer%20ingesting%20(BLI)%20ducted%20fans%20and%20operate%20adjacent%20to%20the%20fuselage%20or%20wing%2C%20ingesting%20the%20boundary%20layer%20flow.%20This%20technology%20is%20integral%20to%20several%20future%20aircraft%2C%20such%20as%20ONERA%E2%80%99s%20NOVA%2C%20the%20NASA%2FMIT%20Aurora%20D8%2C%20Airbus%E2%80%99%20Nautilus%20and%20the%20Lilium%20Jet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20does%20the%20groundbreaking%20study%20his%20team%20recently%20published%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Fluid%20Mechanics%20say%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Dr%20Ahmed%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20study%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Bristol%E2%80%99s%20National%20Aeroacoustic%20Wind%20Tunnel%20Facility%20revealed%20the%20fundamental%20mechanisms%20of%20noise%20generation%20from%20these%20BLI%20ducted%20fans.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20identify%20distinct%20noise%20sources%20originating%20from%20the%20duct%2C%20the%20rotating%20fan%2C%20and%20the%20air%20flowing%20over%20the%20curved%20airframe%20surface.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20the%20noise%20pattern%20changes%20depending%20on%20how%20much%20thrust%20the%20fan%20is%20producing.%20When%20the%20fan%20is%20producing%20high%20thrust%2C%20we%20observed%20a%20noise%20pattern%20similar%20to%20what%20is%20seen%20in%20fans%20without%20ducts.%20But%20when%20the%20fan%20is%20producing%20less%20thrust%2C%20the%20noise%20pattern%20changes%20because%20the%20duct%20itself%20starts%20making%20more%20noise.%20By%20understanding%20the%20source%20of%20noise%20from%20our%20research%2C%20engineers%20can%20decide%20what%20aspects%20of%20noise%20to%20be%20controlled%20and%20they%20can%20make%20effective%20noise%20control%20devices%20accordingly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20understanding%20the%20noise%20mechanisms%20in%20BLI%20ducted%20fans%2C%20Dr%20Ahmed%20also%20hopes%20that%20industrial%20guidelines%20can%20be%20developed%20for%20%E2%80%9Cquieter%20airframe-integrated%20propulsion%20systems%20in%20future%20aircraft%20concepts%E2%80%9D%20from%20large-scale%20conventional%20aircraft%20to%20small-scale%20eVTOL%20aircrafts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFan-article-1719839866.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerospace%20engineer's%20pioneering%20research%20could%20give%20birth%20to%20silent%20aeroplanes%20and%20silent%20flights.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFan-article-1719839866.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFan-article-1719839866-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFan-article-1719839866-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355065%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EElectric%20ducted%20fan%20mounted%20next%20to%20the%20curved%20surface%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIdentifying%20the%20physical%20sources%20of%20noise%20is%20crucial%20for%20effective%20noise%20reduction.%20For%20noise%20reduction%20purposes%2C%20we%20must%20find%20out%20what%20the%20physical%20sources%20are%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThus%20far%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20noise%20suppression%20methods%20or%20devices%20in%20ducted%20fans%20have%20been%20developed%20largely%20on%20a%20trial%20and%20error%20basis.%20It%20is%20hoped%20that%20future%20efforts%20in%20ducted%20fan%20noise%20suppression%20will%20focus%20on%20suppressing%20both%20fan%20and%20duct%20noise%20in%20both%20high%20and%20low-thrust%20regimes.%20By%20advancing%20our%20understanding%20of%20these%20noise%20sources%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20development%20of%20more%20precise%20noise%20guidelines%20and%20standards%2C%20thereby%20simplifying%20the%20certification%20process%20for%20future%20aircraft%20technologies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%2C%20led%20by%20Dr%20Feroz%20Ahmed%2C%20was%20organised%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20Professor%20Mahdi%20Azarpeyvand.%20It%20was%20sponsored%20by%20the%20European%20Union%E2%80%99s%20Horizon%202020%20research%20and%20innovation%20programme%20under%20the%20ENODISE%20(Enabling%20optimised%20disruptive%20airframe-propulsion%20integration%20concepts)%20project%20in%20collaboration%20with%20ONERA%2C%20and%20other%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsilent-flight-edges-cl-1-1719839067.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Ahmed%20comes%20up%20with%20research%20for%20silent%20flights%20on%20aeroplanes%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsilent-flight-edges-cl-1-1719839067.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsilent-flight-edges-cl-1-1719839067-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsilent-flight-edges-cl-1-1719839067-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsilent-flight-edges-cl-1-1719839067-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsilent-flight-edges-cl-1-1719839067-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355053%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBoundary%20layer%20ingesting%20(BLI)%20ducted%20fan%20test%20rig%20inside%20the%20aeroacoustics%20wind%20tunnel%20facility%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Bristol%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Ladakh%20to%20Bristol%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%20family%20with%20modest%20means%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282723%2Fbest-homestays-in-ladakh-things-to-do-in-leh-local-experience%2F%5C%22%3ELeh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr%20Ahmed%20never%20thought%20in%20a%20million%20years%20that%20he%20would%20one%20day%20be%20working%20on%20groundbreaking%20research%20projects%20in%20modern%20aviation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20parents%2C%20Haji%20Haleem%20and%20Zahra%20Bano%2C%20were%20originally%20from%20Kargil%20but%20moved%20to%20Leh%20in%20the%20early%201980s%20in%20search%20of%20better%20livelihood%20opportunities.%C2%A0In%20the%20Skampari%20area%20of%20Leh%2C%20Dr%20Ahmed%20grew%20up%20alongside%20children%20from%20other%20migrant%20communities%20from%20Kargil%20and%20Nubra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20(formally)%20illiterate%2C%20his%20parents%20were%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20that%20Dr%20Ahmed%20and%20his%20six%20siblings%20received%20a%20quality%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20started%20as%20a%20construction%20labourer%2C%20taught%20himself%20mathematics%20and%20gradually%20worked%20his%20way%20up%20to%20supervisor%20before%20eventually%20becoming%20a%20construction%20contractor%20in%20Leh.%20I%20was%20born%20when%20my%20father%20was%20transitioning%20from%20construction%20supervisor%20to%20contractor%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20father%E2%80%99s%20journey%2C%20achieved%20without%20any%20formal%20education%2C%20deeply%20inspired%20him.%20During%20Dr%20Ahmed%E2%80%99s%20childhood%2C%20his%20father%20often%20took%20him%20to%20construction%20sites%20on%20weekends.%20There%2C%20he%20was%20exposed%20to%20practical%20engineering%20and%20interacted%20closely%20with%20workers%20and%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20memorable%20experiences%20greatly%20influenced%20my%20early%20academic%20development%2C%20particularly%20my%20passion%20for%20mathematics%20and%20physics.%20I%20credit%20this%20early%20exposure%20and%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20inspiring%20journey%20for%20my%20strong%20foundation%20in%20these%20subjects%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20his%20interest%20in%20becoming%20an%20aerospace%20engineer%20developed%20while%20he%20was%20studying%20in%20Leh%20and%20Jammu.%20%E2%80%9CUnlike%20other%20students%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20take%20the%20conventional%20route%20in%20engineering.%20Most%20students%20end%20up%20going%20for%20electrical%2C%20civil%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F264506%2Fnew-zealand-best-dosa-ktichen-venu-jagarul-south-indian-restaurant%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emechanical%20engineering%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20explore%20something%20different%20and%20aerospace%20engineering%20caught%20my%20interest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20obtaining%20his%20undergraduate%20degree%20in%20Aeronautical%20Engineering%20at%20Punjab%20Engineering%20College%20(PEC)%20Chandigarh%20in%202012%2C%20he%20was%20selected%20to%20study%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F287506%2Fiisc-bengaluru-reuse-upcycle-old-decommissioned-solar-panels-as-building-material%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(IISc)%20%3C%2Fa%3EBengaluru%2C%20for%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20Aerospace%20Engineering.%20For%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20thesis%2C%20he%20did%20research%20on%20a%20Reusable%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(RLV)%20using%20experiments%20in%20wind%20tunnels.%20His%20thesis%20was%20supported%20by%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(ISRO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ahmed%E2%80%99s%20time%20at%20IISc%20was%20a%20turning%20point.%20His%20thesis%20was%20awarded%20an%20outstanding%20grade%20(awarded%208%2F8%20GPA)%2C%20and%20the%20research%20outcome%20was%20later%20published%20and%20presented%20at%20an%20international%20conference.%20He%20credits%20his%20thesis%20supervisor%20Dr%20SB%20Kandagal%20at%20IISc%20for%20moulding%20him%20into%20a%20good%20researcher.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20profound%20journey%20at%20IISc%20showed%20me%20the%20way%20to%20move%20forward%20towards%20research%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20was%20at%20this%20institution%20where%20I%20discovered%20my%20passion%20for%20solving%20problems%20in%20complex%20engineering%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%2C%20Dr%20Ahmed%20spent%20four%20years%20in%20the%20aerospace%20industry%20and%20academia%20as%20an%20engineer%20and%20assistant%20professor%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20further%20expanding%20his%20skills%20and%20practical%20knowledge.%20His%20growing%20interest%20in%20conducting%20deeper%20research%20led%20him%20to%20pursue%20a%20PhD%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F308072%2Fbrimful-of-asha-cornershop-tribute-by-immigrant-son-tijinder-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20Kingdom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20was%20accepted%20into%20a%20competitive%20four-year%20doctoral%20programme%20at%20University%20College%20London%20(UCL).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20Petroleum%2C%20a%20British%20multinational%20oil%20and%20gas%20company%2C%20and%20the%20Engineering%20and%20Physical%20Science%20Research%20Council%20(EPSRC)%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20funded%20his%20PhD%20through%20the%20Industrial%20Cooperative%20Awards%20in%20Science%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%20(iCASE)%20programme.%20To%20cover%20his%20tuition%20fees%20and%20monthly%20salaries%2C%20a%20scholarship%20of%20%C2%A3180%2C000%20was%20awarded%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ahmed%20completed%20his%20PhD%20in%20September%202022%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20his%20career%20as%20a%20researcher%20and%20engineer%2C%20ready%20to%20contribute%20innovative%20solutions%20to%20the%20field%20of%20aerospace%20engineering.%20Based%20on%20high-quality%20research%20output%20during%20his%20PhD%2C%20he%20was%20granted%20a%20United%20Kingdom%20Global%20Talent%20visa%2C%20endorsed%20by%20UK%20Research%20and%20Innovation%20(UKRI)%20and%20started%20working%20as%20a%20researcher%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Bristol%20on%201%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20institutions%20in%20India%20opened%20many%20doors%20for%20me%2C%20my%20research%20work%20took%20off%20in%20the%20UK.%20I%20feel%20more%20work%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20support%20and%20encourage%20quality%20research%20work%20in%20India.%20There%20are%20many%20scientists%20and%20engineers%20from%20underprivileged%20and%20underrepresented%20communities%20like%20me%20in%20the%20country%20who%20have%20the%20talent%20to%20do%20high-quality%20research%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20requisite%20environment%2C%20and%20social%20and%20institutional%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Dr%20Feroz%20Ahmed%2C%20Wikimedia%20Commons%20and%20University%20of%20Bristol)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Silent%20flight%20edge